                <p>On her first day off she <input type="text" class="blank-input" name="blank1" placeholder="(1)"> to just take it easy <input type="text" class="blank-input" name="blank2" placeholder="(2)"> sleep all day. <input type="text" class="blank-input" name="blank3" placeholder="(3)"> next day she <input type="text" class="blank-input" name="blank4" placeholder="(4)"> up with her friends and partied all night <input type="text" class="blank-input" name="blank5" placeholder="(5)">! The <input type="text" class="blank-input" name="blank6" placeholder="(6)"> morning she <input type="text" class="blank-input" name="blank7" placeholder="(7)"> a horrible headache because she <input type="text" class="blank-input" name="blank8" placeholder="(8)"> forgotten to drink plenty of <input type="text" class="blank-input" name="blank9" placeholder="(9)"> before going to bed. She <input type="text" class="blank-input" name="blank10" placeholder="(10)"> claims <input type="text" class="blank-input" name="blank11" placeholder="(11)"> she <input type="text" class="blank-input" name="blank12" placeholder="(12)"> on a diet! BS I say!</p>
                
                <div style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666;">
                    <strong>Word bank:</strong> took/made/chose/decided, and/to/so/then, A/An/The/Ø, team/go/meet/together, long/through/away/during, milk/cola/water, again/still/yet, like/that/so, am/is/the
                </div>
